ation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.lawbc.com/regulatory-developments/entry/tsca-reform-detailed-summary-of-key-changes-in-frank-r.-lautenberg-chemical\">\"Recent Regulatory Developments | Bergeson &amp; Campbell\"</a>. <i>www.lawbc.com</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2016-02-14</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=www.lawbc.com&amp;rft.atitle=Recent+Regulatory+Developments+%7C+Bergeson+%26+Campbell&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lawbc.com%2Fregulatory-developments%2Fentry%2Ftsca-reform-detailed-summary-of-key-changes-in-frank-r.-lautenberg-chemical&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARegulation+of+chemicals\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://thomas.loc.gov/cgi-bin/bdquery/D?d114:1:./temp/~bdeNWG:@@@R/home/LegislativeData.php\">\"HR 2576 Frank R. Lautenberg Chemical Safety for the 21st Century Act\"</a>. Library of Congress<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">June 22,</span> 2016</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=HR+2576+Frank+R.+Lautenberg+Chemical+Safety+for+the+21st+Century+Act&amp;rft.pub=Library+of+Congress&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fthomas.loc.gov%2Fcgi-bin%2Fbdquery%2FD%3Fd114%3A1%3A.%2Ftemp%2F~bdeNWG%3A%40%40%40R%2Fhome%2FLegislativeData.php&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARegulation+of+chemicals\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-11\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-11